{
  "title": "CentOS 7 (RHEL 7)服务管理命令的变化",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<embed id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" type=\"application/thunder_download_plugin\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><h1 class=\"entry-title\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, 'Nimbus Sans L', sans-serif; line-height: 1.3em; font-size: 21px;\">CentOS 7 (RHEL 7)服务管理命令的变化</h1><div class=\"entry-meta\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, Helvetica, 'Nimbus Sans L', sans-serif; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px;\"><span class=\"meta-prep meta-prep-author\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">发表于</span><a href=\"http://www.ebanban.com/?p=476\" title=\"14:08\" rel=\"bookmark\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\"><span class=\"entry-date\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">2014年10月23日</span></a><span class=\"meta-sep\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">由</span><span class=\"author vcard\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a class=\"url fn n\" href=\"http://www.ebanban.com/?author=2\" title=\"查看所有由daban发布的文章\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119);\">daban</a></span></div><div class=\"entry-content\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 12px 0px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, 'Bitstream Charter', serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;\"><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">CentOS 7 (RHEL 7)带来了新的服务管理命令，为了保持兼容原有的命令仍可以使用，以下是新旧命令的对照。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">启动、停止、重启、重载、检查服务：<br>6: service httpd start|stop|restart|reload|status<br>7: systemctl start|stop|restart|reload|status httpd.service</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">允许、禁止服务自启动：<br>6: chkconfig httpd on|off<br>7: system enable|disable httpd.service</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">列出服务：<br>6: chkconfig –list<br>7: systemctl list-unit-files –type=service 或 ls /etc/systemd/system/*.wants/</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">添加服务：<br>6: chkconfig httpd –add<br>7: systemctl daemon-reload</p></div>"
    }
  ]
}